{{orphan|date=June 2010}} [[File:Koryaks in Russian Federation.png|thumb|270px|Koryaks in Russian Federation]] '''Anapel''' is the goddess of [[reincarnation]] and birth worshipped by the [[Koryak people]] of [[Siberia]]. Her name means "Little Grandmother" in the [[Koryak language]]. She was worshipped at ceremonies following the birth of a new child. ==Sources== *[http://www.godfinder.org/ GodFinder.org] *[http://www.geocities.com/Wellesley/1582/easterng.html Eastern European goddesses] ([https://www.webcitation.org/5kn8BuXjO?url=http://www.geocities.com/Wellesley/1582/easterng.html Archived] 2009-10-25)
